snippet.title: [Solo Leveling:ARISE] Character Teaser #3: Lim Tae-Gyu
snippet.description:
✨[Solo Leveling:ARISE]✨ 

The master of [Fiend] Guild, Korea's very first guild.
His expertise lies in ranged attacks using magic arrows!

"I never miss a shot"
Check out the teaser of S-rank hunter 'Lim Tae-Gyu'!

Want to learn more? Then keep a lookout for updates on our official channels:
